      "title": "CSE shows significant improvement as ASPI gains over 205 points",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Stock Exchange (CSE) showed significant improvement today (August 31) as the All Share Price Index (ASPI) gained 205.92 points to close at 9,071.32 points.",
        "Meanwhile, the S&P SL20 index also moved up by 66.22 points to close at 2,928.97 points at the end of trading today. This is an increase of 2.31 per cent."
      ],
